shire, Wales. She married Gwilym ap Dafydd in 1445, in Wentworth, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1425–":"1425–Surnud","1420–1493":"1420–1493","1450–Male":"1450–Surnud","1425–Female":"1425–Surnud","1425":"1425","1445":"1445","1420":"1420","1450":"1450","1493":"1493","Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales":"Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales","Wentworth, Wath Upon Dearne, West Yorkshire, England":"Wentworth, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, England"},"fi":{"1425–":"1425–Kuollut","1420–1493":"1420–1493","1450–Male":"1450–Kuollut","1425–Female":"1425–Kuollut","1425":"1425","1445":"1445","1420":"1420","1450":"1450","1493":"1493","Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales":"Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales","Wentworth, Wath Upon Dearne, West Yorkshire, England":"Wentworth, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, England"},"fr":{"1425–":"1425–Décédée","1420–1493":"1420–1493","1450–Male":"1450–Décédé","1425–Female":"1425–Décédée","1425":"1425","1445":"1445","1420":"1420","1450":"1450","1493":"1493","Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales":"Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Galles","Wentworth, Wath Upon Dearne, West Yorkshire, England":"Wentworth, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Jinkin verch Llewellyn est née en 1425, à Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Galles. Elle a épousé Gwilym ap Dafydd en 1445, à Wentworth, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1425–":"1425–Verstorben","1420–1493":"1420–1493","1450–Male":"1450–Verstorben","1425–Female":"1425–Verstorben","1425":"1425","1445":"1445","1420":"1420","1450":"1450","1493":"1493","Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales":"Ystradfellte, Breconshire, Wales","Wentworth, Wath Upon Dearne, West Yorkshire, England":"Wentworth, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom","Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, England","lifeSummary":